&nbsp; The police have arrested 48 foreigners said to have been hiding in a house in Githurai Kimbo, Kiambu County. The aliens, of Ethiopian origin, were were arrested in Ruiru yesterday. Ruiru OCPD Isaac Thuranira said his officers pounced on the foreigners after a tip off from the public. &quot;We swiftly moved and arrested them to avert any criminal activity they may have planned,&quot; he said. &quot;They were in a small single room where they were staying. Some had fainted due to lack of enough oxygen,&quot; Thuranira said and warned locals against&nbsp;harbouring aliens. ALSO READ: Nairobi, Kiambu lead in voter registration